   20: -module(base64_property_test_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   23: -compile([export_all, nowarn_export_all]).
   24: 
   25: all() ->
   26:     [
   27:      encode_case,
   28:      encode_to_string_case,
   29:      decode_case,
   30:      decode_malformed_case,
   31:      decode_noisy_case,
   32:      decode_to_string_case,
   33:      decode_to_string_malformed_case,
   34:      decode_to_string_noisy_case,
   35:      mime_decode_case,
   36:      mime_decode_malformed_case,
   37:      mime_decode_to_string_case,
   38:      mime_decode_to_string_malformed_case
   39:     ].
   40: 
   41: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   42:     ct_property_test:init_per_suite(Config).
   43: 
   44: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   45:     Config.
   46: 
   47: encode_case(Config) ->
   48:     do_proptest(prop_encode, Config).
   49: 
   50: encode_to_string_case(Config) ->
   51:     do_proptest(prop_encode_to_string, Config).
   52: 
   53: decode_case(Config) ->
   54:     do_proptest(prop_decode, Config).
   55: 
   56: decode_malformed_case(Config) ->
   57:     do_proptest(prop_decode_malformed, Config).
   58: 
   59: decode_noisy_case(Config) ->
   60:     do_proptest(prop_decode_noisy, Config).
   61: 
   62: decode_to_string_case(Config) ->
   63:     do_proptest(prop_decode_to_string, Config).
   64: 
   65: decode_to_string_malformed_case(Config) ->
   66:     do_proptest(prop_decode_to_string_malformed, Config).
   67: 
   68: decode_to_string_noisy_case(Config) ->
   69:     do_proptest(prop_decode_to_string_noisy, Config).
   70: 
   71: mime_decode_case(Config) ->
   72:     do_proptest(prop_mime_decode, Config).
   73: 
   74: mime_decode_malformed_case(Config) ->
   75:     do_proptest(prop_mime_decode_malformed, Config).
   76: 
   77: mime_decode_to_string_case(Config) ->
   78:     do_proptest(prop_mime_decode_to_string, Config).
   79: 
   80: mime_decode_to_string_malformed_case(Config) ->
   81:     do_proptest(prop_mime_decode_to_string_malformed, Config).
   82: 
   83: do_proptest(Prop, Config) ->
   84:     ct_property_test:quickcheck(
   85:         base64_prop:Prop(),
   86:         Config).
